  <p>Mark Zuckerberg is an American computer programmer and Internet entrepreneur. He co-founded Facebook, now Meta Platforms, Inc., in 2004 with his college roommates Andrew McCollum, Eduardo Saverin, Chris Hughes, and Dustin Moskovitz. Zuckerberg is the chairman and CEO of Meta, overseeing the company's social media empire, which includes Facebook, Instagram, WhatsApp, and Oculus VR.</p>

  <h2 id="accomplishments">Accomplishments</h2>
